drive: create: Usage: _build/macosx64/bin/infinit-drive --create --name NAME --network NETWORK --volume VOLUME [--description DESCRIPTION] [OPTIONS...]

Create a drive (a network and volume pair):

Create options:
  -n [ --name ] arg      Created drive name
  --description arg      Description of drive
  -N [ --network ] arg   Associated network name
  -V [ --volume ] arg    Associated volume name
  -i [ --icon ] arg      Path to an image to use as icon
  --push-drive           Push the created drive to the Hub
  -p [ --push ]          Alias for --push-drive


